  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a large skillet over medium heat. Add chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in cumin, coriander, turmeric, and cayenne pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add chicken broth and bring to a boil. Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add split potato buns to the skillet and simmer for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in Greek yogurt and cook for 2-3 minutes, or until heated through.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve hot."
  ],
